re alexis m herman chair and chief executive officer new ventures llc alexis herman has been a director of the cocacola company since  ms herman is the chair and chief executive officer of new ventures llc a corporate consulting company and has held these positions since  she served as chair of the business advisory board of sodexo inc an integrated food and facilities management services company through  and serves as a member of toyota motor corporations diversity advisory board and global advisory board as chair of the companys human resources task force from  to  ms herman worked with the company to identify ways to improve its human resources policies and practices following the november  settlement of an employment lawsuit from  to  she served as us secretary of labor she is also a director of cummins inc entergy corporation and mgm resorts international related items our company related posts board of directors operations leadership senior leadership our workplace the cocacola company recommends human  workplace rights how we achieve success is as important as the success itself the cocacola company recommends health  safety we are focused on the safety of our employees our visitors and the public sustainability report the fizz most read top  back  why sea glass collectors cherish coke bottles  is your name on a coke bottle  labelless cocacola cans tackle prejudice during ramadan  cocacola cake recipe  relationships matter why cokes muhtar kent never dines alone  the delicious dozen the  best cocacolas i ever tasted  cocacola ribs or chicken wings recipe  cocacola life arrives on shelves nationwide  share a coke  the hit campaign is back and it’s bigger and better than ever  the real story of new coke back most shared top  back  step inside new cocacola india offices  labelless cocacola cans tackle prejudice during ramadan  relationships matter why cokes muhtar kent never dines alone  run commuting takes off in cities around the world  fresh banana cake with 