y other time in our history we have to know that staying in school and getting an education is the most important thing you can do alexis herman education time history the public sector certainly includes the department of labor those are jobs that are available they are open and they are good paying jobs the government as a whole has been actually retrenching under president clintons leadership alexis herman leadership good government we have had actually a decline in government service overall but the growth is in hightech areas specialty areas in the labor department and other departments alexis herman growth service government to me it is a process a process that starts with raising awareness engaging international partners on this issue and being committed to a different course of action alexis herman action process awareness but the real growth i must say in terms of the public sector for the labor department is really at state and local levels thats where the real opportunities are today alexis herman today growth opportunities my overall message for labor members is that we understand that the benefits of trade are clear but the disruption and the dislocation are painfully concentrated and we cant ignore them alexis herman understand clear labor the fact of the matter is this is a very dynamic economy we have and in this dynamic economy you have a lot of job gains but you also have job loss alexis herman job loss matter this can not be about a race to the bottom alexis herman race bottom about it is very important that our young people have constructive early work experiences but it is equally important that their jobs are safe and complement their education rather than complete it alexis herman work education people share this page cite this page citation find on amazon alexis herman related authors elizabeth warren clara barton eric holder j edgar hoover alexander haig jim garrison john foster dulles ramsey clark brainyquote desktop brainyquote mobile site